nodes.bodyText:
I'm a little concerned that even though this is temporary, consumers can easily incorrectly add clusters. What do you think about doing something like this:
private var virtualClusters = [String]()

func addVirtualCluster(_ virtualCluster: String) -> EnvoyClientBuilder {
  self.virtualClusters.append(virtualCluster)
  return self
}

Then later you can pass it down as "[\(self.virtualClusters.joined(separator: ",")]"
WDYT?
